l Muluk]] Lake\n* [[Lulusar]] Lake\n* [[Dudipatsar]] Lake\n* [[Pyala Lake]]\n{{commons category|Naran}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in Mansehra District]]\n[[Category:Tourist attractions in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]]\n", "text_old": "{{refimprove|date=January 2018}}\n\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n| name                    = Naran\n| native_name             = {{nq|\u0646\u0627\u0631\u0627\u0646}}\n| native_name_lang        = ur\n| settlement_type         = [[Town]]\n| image_skyline           = File:Entrance of Naran..jpg \n| image_alt               = \n| image_caption           = Naran Town\n| ag              = \n| flag_alt                = \n| image_seal              = \n| seal_alt                = \n| image_shield            = \n| shield_alt              = \n| nickname                = \n| motto                   = \n| image_map               = \n| map_alt                 = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_map             = Khyber Pakhtunkhwa#Pakistan\n| pushpin_label_position  = left\n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| pushpin_map_caption     = \n| coordinates             = {{Coord|34|54|22|N|73|38|58|E|type:city_region:PK|display=inline,title}}\n| coor_pinpoint           = \n| coordinates_footnotes   = \n| subdivision_type        = Country\n| subdivision_name        = {{flagicon|PAK}}[[Pakistan]]\n| subdivision_type1       = [[Provinces of Pakistan|Province]]\n| subdivision_name1       = [[Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]]\n| subdivision_type2       = [[List of districts of Pakistan|District]]\n| subdivision_name2       = [[Mansehra District|Mansehra]]\n| subdivision_type3       = \n| subdivision_name3       = \n| established_title       = \n| established_date        = \n| founder                 = \n| seat_type               = \n| seat                    = \n| government_footnotes    = \n| leader_party            = \n| leader_title            = \n| leader_name      